data.description: Have you been searching for a nice sized home and acreage for your family? This 4 bedroom, 2 bath home on 4.79 acres may be the perfect spot for you. It has a large kitchen with breakfast bar island, and dining room area. There are family and living room areas, so everyone has space to relax. The master suite is spacious, with a nice walk-in closet and master bath features dual sinks, a garden tub and walk-in shower. There is a large open deck out front to sit enjoy the nicely treed yard. It's located near the end of a dead-end street, so you won't be bothered with much road noise. You'll be just a short drive into town for schools, shopping and restaurants. The Nature Coast State Trail for biking, hiking or jogs is just around the corner and you'll also be not too far from several State Parks with cool springs and the Suwannee River. Make some time to see this one soon!
